@startuml
title Detailed support request lifecycle
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
actor Operator
participant "RequestList.vue" as list_view
participant "SupportRequestForm.vue" as form
participant "SupportRequestStore" as request_store
participant "RequestDetailModal.vue" as detail_modal
participant "Axios Client" as client
participant "SupportRequestsController" as sr_controller
participant "CommentsController" as comments_controller
participant "SupportRequest" as sr_model
participant "Comment" as comment_model
database "SQLite" as db

Operator -> list_view: Open create/edit request
list_view -> form: Show side panel
Operator -> form: Fill title, description, priority, assignee
form -> request_store: createRequest/updateRequest(payload)
request_store -> client: POST/PATCH /support_requests
client -> sr_controller: route action
sr_controller -> sr_model: save/update
sr_model -> db: INSERT/UPDATE support_requests
db --> sr_model: persisted record
sr_model --> sr_controller: payload
sr_controller --> client: JSON response
client --> request_store: request data
request_store --> list_view: refresh list
list_view --> Operator: show updated request

Operator -> detail_modal: Open request details
detail_modal -> request_store: fetchRequest(id)
request_store -> client: GET /support_requests/:id
client -> sr_controller: show
sr_controller -> sr_model: load request + comments
sr_model -> db: SELECT request and comments
db --> sr_model: associated rows
sr_model --> sr_controller: enriched payload
sr_controller --> client: JSON response
client --> request_store: current request
request_store --> detail_modal: display details

Operator -> detail_modal: Add comment
detail_modal -> request_store: addComment(id, payload)
request_store -> client: POST /support_requests/:id/comments
client -> comments_controller: create
comments_controller -> comment_model: save
comment_model -> db: INSERT comment
db --> comment_model: created comment
comment_model --> comments_controller: comment object
comments_controller --> client: JSON response
client --> request_store: new comment
request_store --> detail_modal: append to comments list
@enduml
